title: 15-Minute Walk-Run Intervals | Follow Along Treadmill Workout!
description:
🏃‍♀️ Elevate your fitness routine with this quick yet effective 15-minute treadmill walk-run workout! Join Coach Rachael as she guides you through a series of intervals, seamlessly blending walking and running to maximize calorie burn and boost cardiovascular endurance. Whether you're a beginner or looking for a quick energy boost, this session is tailored for all levels to help you achieve your fitness goals efficiently. 🔥 Hit play, follow along, and stride towards a healthier you!

15 minutes of run and recovery intervals

All speeds and inclines are suggestions. Please stay safe and within your comfort zone!

comments: More like these please!!! Loved it.

I usually can hold 7 comfortably and push myself to 8+ but I did this one at 8 the whole time and even pushed to 9 on the last one! I’m actually improving and it’s all thanks to Rachel and the IBX family!!

I've been doing 12. 3. 40 and then my cool down is this workout. I have to play your video and follow along. No idea how you can talk while doing this. I huff and puff 🤣 I'm like how is she talking! Lol but thank you for this workout. It's my cool down I feel amazing after. One day at a time.  As a mom the 15 minutes are definitely me time! Time for myself to focus mentally and physically.
She’s awesome, I really enjoy your motivational talk!! Thank you ♥️
